<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.2">
<l>muṉiyāy vantu mūveḻukāl muṭicēr maṉṉa ruṭaltuṇiya</l>
<l>taṉivāy maḻuviṉ paṭaiyāṇṭa tārār tōḷāṉ vārpuṟavil</l>
<l>paṉicēr mullai pallarumpap pāṉa lorupāl kaṇkāṭṭa</l>
<l>naṉicēr kamalam mukaṅkāṭṭum naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with wreath-covered shoulders who, coming as a sage,</l>
<l rend="indent">used an axe weapon with a unique edge</l>
<l>To slash the bodies of crowned warriors on three[-times-]seven occasions,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where profusely gathered lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">show their faces,</l>
<l>As dewy jasmines bud [as] teeth in the wide woodlands and, at [their] side,</l>
<l rend="indent">blue lotuses show their eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
